# Installation

## Requirements

- Python {{ python_version | default('3.8+') }}
- pip or uv package manager

## Install from PyPI

```bash
pip install {{ project_slug }}
```

## Install from Source

```bash
git clone {{ repo_url }}
cd {{ project_slug }}
pip install -e .
```

## Development Installation

```bash
git clone {{ repo_url }}
cd {{ project_slug }}
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```

## Verify Installation

```python
import {{ project_slug }}
print({{ project_slug }}.__version__)
```

